steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591450/extras/f1e16e9aff55050529928c0128a22986.avif?t=1723790883\" width=580 height=80 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Relaxation</strong></h2>Relaxing in hot springs with monkeys, watching clouds while listening to the ocean waves, or taking a nap on a giant Capybara...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591450/extras/a238c87a82a56dee7d8186d057bd2710.poster.avif?t=1723790883\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591450/extras/a238c87a82a56dee7d8186d057bd2710.webm?t=1723790883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591450/extras/a238c87a82a56dee7d8186d057bd2710.mp4?t=1723790883\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Narrative quests</strong></h2>Aka isn't a linear game. Meet various characters of all kinds: villagers willing to help, trapped animals, giant monsters, or ghosts from your past who need your help to be freed.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591450/extras/aec87ec2c30759fb539c9eb3ff6b755f.poster.avif?t=1723790883\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591450/extras/aec87ec2c30759fb539c9eb3ff6b755f.webm?t=1723790883\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591450/extras/aec87ec2c30759fb539c9eb3ff6b755f.mp4?t=1723790883\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Mini-games</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_i